Description: [b]I[/b]t's a old fashioned key... I woke up with it, but don't know where it goes. Touching it feels... calming for some reason. It has [color=yellow] GAS STATION [/color] etched on it.
[b]I[/b] can't remember ever being without my journal. Lately though, there are entries in it I don't remember writing... but it's in my handwriting...
[b]N[/b]ot much use when the car doesn't work...
